room_title: Escape room "Space Pirates" by Epic Escape Game in Muncie
room_description:
Star Fleet 9000 is the newest intergalactic cruise ship the galaxy has produced visiting colonized planets such as Mars, Jupiter and Saturnâ€™s moon Titan. During your space cruise to Titan, your ship has been taken over by Space Pirates.
They have seized control of the ship's systems and taken the ship's most valuable resource: the Ionic Propulsion Cells. Without this, the ship will drift aimlessly. The pirates have locked all guests in the ships holding bay. You must repair your ship, replace the Propulsion Cells and escape the clutches of the Space Pirates.
